Package oracle.apps.fnd.applcore.dt.patterns.piLayout.gui

Custom Classes relating to property inspector Gui.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
BaseGuiComponent Base Custom Gui Component, extended by applicationsTable, applicationsTree and applicationsTreeTable.
BaseGuiPanel Class that acts as a Gui Panel for use in the table custom gui component in the property inspector.
ButtonAttributes Class that acts as a generic bean to hold attributes for a button in a DC to be shown in a PI custom gui.
ButtonGuiFieldLayout A Panel for showing button attributes for using inside a tabbed layout of a PI custom gui.
ButtonGuiFieldLayoutContainerSearch Class that acts allows search in custom gui components containing tables.
CommonTabAttributes Class that acts as a generic bean to hold attributes for a button in a DC to be shown in a PI custom gui.
CustomGuiField Provides a custom field for editing XMLEF Element attributes.
GenericAttributeValueItem Provides a generic immutable bean representing a single item to be used by XMLEF in a AttributeValueItemProvider.
ListGuiFieldLayout A Panel for showing button attributes for using inside a tabbed layout of a PI custom gui.
RecordNavigationItemProvider Provides a list of record navigation items used by XMLEF.
StyleGuiComponent Gui Component for style info.
TabbedGuiContainerSearch Class that acts allows search in custom gui components containing tabs.
TabbedTableGuiContainerSearch Class that acts allows search in custom gui components containing tables in tabs.
TabTableSearchableLabel Class that acts as a bean containing a searchable label, the table in which it lives and the index of the tab the table is within.
TabTableSearchableLabels Class that acts as a container for TabTableSearchableLabels.
UpdatableTabPanel An abstract panel that introduces behavior for updatig UI based on XMLEF model changes, and resetting UI after navigation changes within that UI.
